{"blocks":[{"key":"7fqf0","text":"Wash silica wafers with ddH2O and acetone for three times.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sub","offset":27,"length":1}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fkb57","text":"Incubate the silica wafers in fixation solution (2.5% glutaraldehyde in 1X PBS) at  overnight.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":82,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"5v795","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"1B27ADD0486711EDA9B22F8F4B1F6D76","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"4","unit":10}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5rnbv","text":"Incubate the samples in ethanol solution with an increasing concentration (40%, 70%, 96%, 100%) for   each concentration.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":100,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"4kste","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":3600,"guid":"83A30BA0486911EDA9B22F8F4B1F6D76","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}
